                每个用户可以获得<asp:TextBox ID="tbnumber" runat="server" CssClass="input normal" datatype="n"
                    sucmsg=" " Text="1" />张券</dd>
        </dl>
        <dl>
            <dt>有效时间：</dt>
            <dd>
                <asp:TextBox ID="tbstime" runat="server" CssClass="input date" onfocus="stime()"
